The Idaho open floor plan display's the beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and rich cabinets with crown molding. It's open to a large living and dining area. Three spacious bedrooms and a loft with two and 1/2 baths. Primary bedroom is downstairs with large walk in closet, Primary bathroom w double vanity and large shower. Please visit our Model Home located at 7876 Enchanted Park Dr., El Paso, TX 79911 Open Daily 10am-5:30pm
Photos are for demonstration purposes and not of actual home.
Ready for a new buyer!
